I '''Farid F. Abraham''' (mibait Mayu 5, 1937) metung yang [[United States|American]]ung scientist.

I Abraham ikua ne ing kayang [[Bachelor of Science]] ampong [[Doctor of Philosophy|Ph.D]] king  [[University ning Arizona]] inyang 1959 ampong 1962, mitukituki. Kapamilatan ning pamanimuna keng makabayung paralan a gagamit modelling keng pamanyalugsug, mekaambag ya keng science keng marangle ning  [[fracture mechanics]], membrane dynamics ampong [[phase change|phase transformation]] galo da reng  [[bage]]. Atlu ya sinulat a aklat (libru) ampong maiggit a 200 sulat a melimbag kareng international journals, kayabe no reng atlu articulu keng ''[[Science (journal)|Science]]''.  
Menyambut yang galal a  [[Aneesur Rahman]] keng computational physics,
a nung nu iti ingn pekamatas a galal a binie ning [[American Physical Society]].

